{"id":"812790055112507392","type":"text","timestamp":1775137000,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/812790055112507392","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/biblicallyaccuratemoth/811332996793761792\">biblicallyaccuratemoth</a>:</p><blockquote><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"3900\" data-orig-width=\"2000\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/794649b212f91f9f2df0cb57e722f924/c547874d7678c167-1f/s640x960/81c619903dca38975e4408b6e3251c422996af95.png\" data-orig-height=\"3900\" data-orig-width=\"2000\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/794649b212f91f9f2df0cb57e722f924/c547874d7678c167-1f/s75x75_c1/cb6f84580dc9274fb58de96525e524cba37208de.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/794649b212f91f9f2df0cb57e722f924/c547874d7678c167-1f/s100x200/8f76d7edfcf421a5a0eec9939e7bdc94a11bb2f6.png 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/794649b212f91f9f2df0cb57e722f924/c547874d7678c167-1f/s250x400/c53ddf41f7bbad6bf8d02c8749ef9a9eb9f7b1bf.png 205w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/794649b212f91f9f2df0cb57e722f924/c547874d7678c167-1f/s400x600/f35b577ef68f35f4838d40b2c614127395070609.png 308w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/794649b212f91f9f2df0cb57e722f924/c547874d7678c167-1f/s500x750/f7d14aa606edc26794284fa8c06672287c87264b.png 385w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/794649b212f91f9f2df0cb57e722f924/c547874d7678c167-1f/s540x810/3791aa710bd8d921ca123ee434ad1a1d38d71924.png 415w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/794649b212f91f9f2df0cb57e722f924/c547874d7678c167-1f/s640x960/81c619903dca38975e4408b6e3251c422996af95.png 492w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/794649b212f91f9f2df0cb57e722f924/c547874d7678c167-1f/s1280x1920/6a75da6ed933da97ba3729536dc92cee7a7170ce.png 985w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/794649b212f91f9f2df0cb57e722f924/c547874d7678c167-1f/s2048x3072/8e4d3dda8d283e5aeede0424767da0d8424a6e02.png 1575w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"/></figure></div><p>I&rsquo;m another year older today. Every version of me that came before would be proud.</p><p>I originally had a plan for a longer comic to celebrate my birthday, but I didn&rsquo;t get started on anything until like&hellip;a week or two ago. And by that point, there was no chance I could get a multi-page project ready. So I shelved the script I had written for later and threw this together, both as a celebration of birth and also as a celebration of the wonderful trans community. As times get tough, remember that community is often the key to survival. Keep each other safe.</p><p>All the creators who cameo on this page are:</p><p><a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/MRzRUOEQfiloUuHNSTw9keQ\">@mystery-incorporated-whore</a></p><p><a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/M2_xBwg5s82oM24VcGlwchg\">@nooodlesartstyle</a></p><p><a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/MUK1jtRJNXtUh2xx0sHGbmg\">@darcyisspidey</a></p><p><a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/MPe2Xy7Cs5EEJKsejquXVug\">@lilyfaewood</a></p><p><a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/MDTxqdX1_lc9tKU9H20AOlg\">@milkypancakess</a></p><p><a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/MlKRiujclp0xHhhmSqA_3Ng\">@ariathelamia</a></p><p><a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/MaA-OXeup724Ir9lJ0Rx_iA\">@pennymations</a></p><p><a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/M_5bYfowP47M_BXJNCtp01Q\">@maxine302</a></p><p><a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/M3Qkpp8jm_EsulUTRNPhlLQ\">@liddimothie</a></p><p><a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/MksdfixwC7mr8ggFt9GwlbQ\">@welldrawnfish</a></p><p><a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/MpIJ3hCyT2b_hrWk6m0aZMA\">@lambinajam</a></p><p><a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/MkCkdfrEJyLQRV-0MbY1xig\">@alice-arty</a></p><p><a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/MO7xUQLDKgKrWoWPqUKOdww\">@squiretilde</a></p><p><a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/MC0f-zV_9NbVDWk